{"tid":2332564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜：武漢肺炎在英國出現變種，防疫措施提升級別！","createTime":"2020-12-19T17:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T23:19:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"90700b987ce7a058f548e53eaa8fe7347dcab081","tid":2332564,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T17:10:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566222-20201220.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566222-20201220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=fd3b6f62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566222-20201220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0cc08692\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566222-20201220.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜透露，現時在英國東南部出現的武漢肺炎出現變種。<br />\n<br />\n他舉行記者會講述英國最新的防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜重申，沒有證據顯示變種的武漢肺炎引致更嚴重病徵及更高死亡率。<br />\n<br />\n他形容，變種病毒可能較以前的病毒，有7成以上傳播能力，但數據仍屬初步，須作出進一步評估。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜表示，倫敦及英格蘭東部等地區將進入新一輪防疫限制，級別升至第四級，聖誕節安排將不一樣。"},{"pid":"2d731c6e7ba9411cb1e3ab3d9cd580b3cf938224","tid":2332564,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"上次好似係D614 -&gt; G614 <br />\n唔知今次會變成點 。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 唔識，都係聽返黎。"},{"pid":"e7fa324ff3fb41e4d79615112a5b2f14b3e59baa","tid":2332564,"uid":171107,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"好似全球都變左種，今次同上幾次比隻毒惡左好多"},{"pid":"a649ee7a7bf9b7b488a3abfa84377a4f49c6a856","tid":2332564,"uid":409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T17:32:10.000Z","msg":"Tier4係咪唔比人入倫敦？"},{"pid":"f012374608d9d68007c8e1a566f34f8e5f44be76","tid":2332564,"uid":53577,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"